<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <title>B-Productive</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main
      class="container-fluid bg-primary-subtle d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center"
    >
      <h1>B-Productive</h1>
      <p>
        Welcome to B-Productive, a productivity app designed to help you stay
        focused and organized. Here are some tips to get you started:
      </p>
      <div>
        <ul>
          <li>Set specific, achievable goals for your tasks</li>
          <li>Break tasks into smaller, manageable steps</li>
          <li>Use a timer to track your progress</li>
          <li>Create a daily to-do list to keep track of your tasks</li>
          <li>Set reminders and notifications to help you stay on track</li>
          <li>Review and adjust your productivity habits as needed</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Stay focused, organized, and productive with B-Productive!</p>
      </div>

      <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button">
        <a href="/app/todo-lists/new" class="text-light">Start</a>
      </button>
    </main>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.8/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-I7E8VVD/ismYTF4hNIPjVp/Zjvgyol6VFvRkX/vR+Vc4jQkC+hVqc2pM8ODewa9r"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-0pUGZvbkm6XF6gxjEnlmuGrJXVbNuzT9qBBavbLwCsOGabYfZo0T0to5eqruptLy"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
